director [words indistinct] and member of the bank's Board of 
Directors, and [words indistinct]. They reported to the rest of 
the banks on the nature of [words indistinct]. The foreign 
exchange rate should be established by the market itself. The 
media would do well in reporting that the BCV has not proposed 
the creation of a secondary exchange market [words indistinct]. 
[end recording] 

