"the student was shot by unidentified individuals from a passing 
vehicle." Two other students also were reported to have been 
wounded by gunfire. After Sotillo was shot and killed, students 
threw rocks at police, who responded by firing tear gas grenades 
into the crowd to disperse the demonstrators.] 

